These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, fanta, milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, electronic, rock
1. the fan of electronic is the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking milk is between the fan of rock and the person drinking fanta##2
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | fanta | milk | mirinda |
| Music-Genre   | electronic     | blues    | rock   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking, hiking
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, police-officer, designer
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the designer is between the fisherman and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | cooking    | hiking        | filmmaking |
| Job     | police-officer | designer | fisherman         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, coffee
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, fish, rabbit
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is between the owner of the fish and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | lemonade     | coffee |
| Pet        | fish  | rabbit | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, salsa, blues
3 different pets are kept: pony, chinchilla, rat
1. the fan of ambient is the owner of the pony##1
2. the fan of blues is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the pony##2
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | blues     | ambient |
| Pet           | chinchilla | rat | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, board-games, filmmaking
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, lizard
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | board-games | filmmaking     | puzzles |
| Pet     | lizard    | goldfish | hamster    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, polish, nigerian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, lacrosse, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is golf is between the nigerian and the turkish##2
2. the turkish is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the polish is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | turkish  | polish   | nigerian        |
| Sport         | lacrosse | golf | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: peas, apple, mango
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, japanese, canadian
1. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating peas##1
2. the russian is between the person eating mango and the japanese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | apple  | peas  | mango |
| Nationality   | japanese | russian | canadian     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, thriller, fantasy
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, japanese, turkish
1. the person watching thriller movies is the turkish##1
2. the japanese is between the person watching thriller movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | scientific  | thriller  |
| Nationality   | dutch | japanese | turkish |

