.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, climbing
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, tram, train
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person driving the roller is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | climbing | cricket | rowing  |
| Transport   | train    | roller        | tram |

