.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, cola
There 3 different types of food: potato, orange, cauliflower
1. the person eating cauliflower is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person eating potato##2
2. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | hot-chocolate      | cola      |
| Food       | orange  | cauliflower | potato |

