.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, 7up, fanta
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, jazz, reggae
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking fanta and the fan of jazz##2
3. the fan of blues is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | fanta | 7up   | cola |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | blues | jazz   |

 